{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja template for MA active-target selection pipeline diagnostics. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.26.1 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-26 #}

{# =========================
  MA Active-Target Selection Pipeline Diagnostic
  Purpose: explain why input_select.ma_active_target remains none.
  Usage:
    1) Optional refresh actions:
       - script.ma_update_target_options
       - script.ma_auto_select
    2) Paste in Developer Tools -> Template.
    3) Use output to identify options/build/selection gate failures.
  ========================= #}

{% set invalid = ['','none','unknown','unavailable','None', none] %}

{% set active_target = states('input_select.ma_active_target') %}
{% set options = state_attr('input_select.ma_active_target','options') or [] %}
{% set active_valid = active_target not in invalid and active_target in options and states[active_target] is not none %}

{% set rooms_raw = state_attr('sensor.spectra_ls_rooms_json','rooms_json') | default([], true) %}
{% set rooms = rooms_raw %}
{% if rooms is string %}
  {% set raw_trim = rooms | trim %}
  {% set raw_trim_l = raw_trim | lower %}
  {% if raw_trim_l not in ['unknown','unavailable','none',''] and (raw_trim.startswith('[') or raw_trim.startswith('{')) %}
    {% set parsed = raw_trim | from_json %}
    {% if parsed is sequence and parsed is not string and parsed is not mapping %}
      {% set rooms = parsed %}
    {% elif parsed is mapping %}
      {% set rooms = (parsed.rooms if parsed.rooms is defined else (parsed.result if parsed.result is defined else [])) %}
    {% else %}
      {% set rooms = [] %}
    {% endif %}
  {% else %}
    {% set rooms = [] %}
  {% endif %}
{% elif rooms is mapping %}
  {% set rooms = (rooms.rooms if rooms.rooms is defined else (rooms.result if rooms.result is defined else [])) %}
{% elif rooms is not sequence %}
  {% set rooms = [] %}
{% endif %}

{% set known = namespace(list=[]) %}
{% for r in rooms %}
  {% if r is not none and r.entity is defined and r.entity not in invalid and states[r.entity] is not none %}
    {% set known.list = known.list + [r.entity] %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% set known_targets = known.list | unique | list %}

{% set players = state_attr('sensor.ma_players','result') or [] %}
{% set discovered = namespace(list=[], rejected=[]) %}
{% for p in players %}
  {% set ent = (p.entity_id if p.entity_id is defined else '') %}
  {% set ip = (state_attr(ent,'ip_address') if ent not in invalid else '') or (p.ip_address if p.ip_address is defined else '') %}
  {% if ent not in invalid and (ent | regex_match('^media_player\.')) and states[ent] is not none and ip not in invalid %}
    {% set discovered.list = discovered.list + [ent] %}
  {% else %}
    {% if ent not in invalid %}
      {% set reason = 'missing_state' if states[ent] is none else ('missing_ip' if ip in invalid else 'filtered') %}
      {% set discovered.rejected = discovered.rejected + [ent ~ ':' ~ reason] %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% set discovered_targets = discovered.list | unique | list %}

{% set detected = states('sensor.ma_detected_receiver_entity') %}
{% set detected_valid = detected not in invalid and (detected | regex_match('^media_player\.')) and states[detected] is not none %}

{% set ma_players_count = states('sensor.ma_players') %}
{% set players_ready = ma_players_count not in ['unknown','unavailable',''] and (ma_players_count | int(0)) > 0 %}

{% set selectable = (known_targets + discovered_targets + ([detected] if detected_valid else [])) | unique | list %}

{% set pick_state = (states(detected) | lower) if detected_valid else '' %}
{% set pick_ready = detected_valid and detected in options and pick_state not in ['','unknown','unavailable'] %}

{% set first_active = namespace(ent='') %}
{% for o in options %}
  {% if first_active.ent == '' and o is string and o.startswith('media_player.') and states[o] is not none %}
    {% set st = states(o) | lower %}
    {% if st in ['playing','paused'] %}
      {% set first_active.ent = o %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% set score = 0 %}
{% if players_ready %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if (known_targets | length) > 0 %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if (discovered_targets | length) > 0 %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if detected_valid %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if (options | length) > 1 %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if (selectable | length) > 0 %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if active_valid %}{% set score = score + 1 %}{% endif %}

{% set verdict = 'PASS' if score >= 6 else 'WARN' %}

### MA Active-Target Selection Pipeline Diagnostic
- Result: **{{ verdict }}**
- Score: **{{ score }}/7**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**

### Active target helper state
- `input_select.ma_active_target`: **{{ active_target }}** (valid={{ active_valid }})
- Options count: **{{ options | length }}**
- Options: **{{ options }}**

### Upstream option builders
- `sensor.ma_players` count: **{{ ma_players_count }}** (ready={{ players_ready }})
- Known targets from rooms map: **{{ known_targets if (known_targets | length) > 0 else [] }}**
- Discovered targets from MA players (ip-qualified): **{{ discovered_targets if (discovered_targets | length) > 0 else [] }}**
- Discovered rejects (first 12): **{{ (discovered.rejected[:12]) if (discovered.rejected | length) > 0 else [] }}**
- Detected receiver entity: **{{ detected }}** (valid={{ detected_valid }})
- Selectable candidates (union): **{{ selectable if (selectable | length) > 0 else [] }}**

### Auto-select gate hints
- Pick-ready (`detected receiver in options and state available`): **{{ pick_ready }}**
- First active option (`playing/paused`): **{{ first_active.ent if first_active.ent != '' else 'none' }}**

### Suggested next action
{% if active_valid %}
- Selection pipeline is healthy in this snapshot.
{% elif (options | length) <= 1 and (selectable | length) == 0 %}
- No selectable candidates reached the helper: check `sensor.spectra_ls_rooms_json`, `sensor.ma_players`, and detected receiver state.
{% elif detected_valid and detected not in options %}
- Detected receiver is valid but missing from helper options: rerun `script.ma_update_target_options` and inspect option update automation.
{% elif first_active.ent != '' %}
- Active candidate exists but helper still none: rerun `script.ma_auto_select` and verify override is off.
{% else %}
- Review discovered rejects and room-map entities to identify missing-state or missing-ip qualifiers.
{% endif %}
